```plantuml
@startuml ertis-research_lwm2m-blockchain

actor User

participant "Angular Anomaly App" as AngularApp
participant "Spring Boot Backend" as Backend
participant "Web3j" as Web3j
participant "AnomalyStore Contract" as AnomalyContract
participant "UserStore Contract" as UserContract
participant "ClientStore Contract" as ClientContract
participant "LwM2M Server" as LwM2MServer
participant "Bootstrap Server" as BootstrapServer
participant "LwM2M Client" as LwM2MClient

User -> AngularApp: Access Anomaly Detection UI
AngularApp -> Backend: Request Anomaly Data
Backend -> Web3j: Interact with Smart Contracts
Web3j -> AnomalyContract: Query Anomaly Data
AnomalyContract --> Web3j: Return Anomaly Data
Web3j --> Backend: Return Anomaly Data
Backend --> AngularApp: Send Anomaly Data

User -> AngularApp: Login
AngularApp -> Backend: Validate User with JWT
Backend -> Web3j: Validate User
Web3j -> UserContract: Check User Credentials
UserContract --> Web3j: Return Validation Result
Web3j --> Backend: Return Validation Result
Backend --> AngularApp: Send Validation Result

AngularApp -> Backend: Register New LwM2M Client
Backend -> Web3j: Register Client
Web3j -> ClientContract: Add Client
ClientContract --> Web3j: Confirm Registration
Web3j --> Backend: Confirm Registration
Backend --> AngularApp: Registration Confirmed

LwM2MClient -> LwM2MServer: Send Data
LwM2MServer -> BootstrapServer: Retrieve Security Info
BootstrapServer -> ClientContract: Get Security Configs
ClientContract --> BootstrapServer: Return Security Configs
BootstrapServer --> LwM2MServer: Return Security Info
LwM2MServer --> LwM2MClient: Acknowledge Data

@enduml
```